Hey, Yeyoung High School!

59
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:38,830
Hey, run! Run!

60
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:40,560
Shit. Hurry up!

61
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:44,920
I'll go to your school if you get caught smoking here again!

62
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,870
Okay?

63
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:48,400
