Excuse me.

66
00:04:58,430 --> 00:05:00,110
Are you the one who filed a report?

67
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:03,120
- Yes, I work at an internet cafe here.
- Yes.

68
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:07,540
The security light broke a long time ago, but it's not getting fixed.

69
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:11,180
They're worse at night. They smoke and litter.

70
00:05:11,180 --> 00:05:13,350
Yes, of course.

71
00:05:13,350 --> 00:05:14,710
I'm sorry. We'll take care of it immediately.

72
00:05:14,710 --> 00:05:17,910
It smells a lot here, and it's hard to clean, too.

73
00:05:17,910 --> 00:05:19,510
The owner always yells at me.

74
00:05:19,510 --> 00:05:21,330
I see.

75
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:23,850
We'll take care of it immediately.

76
00:05:24,550 --> 00:05:26,400
I'm so sorry for the inconvenience.

77
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:29,460
We'll take care of it immediately. I promise.

78
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:32,080
Okay. Carry on, then.

79
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,600
Yes.

80
00:05:36,850 --> 00:05:39,850
It will get fixed quickly if we just tell them the barcode on it.

81
00:05:39,850 --> 00:05:41,340
Let's follow the procedure.

82
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:43,030
